# Syncthing Global Ignore Patterns
# Security-focused patterns for development environment sync

# === SELF-HOSTED SECURITY ===
# Since we control our own Syncthing infrastructure, we CAN sync sensitive files
# But still exclude some system-specific or temporary sensitive files

# Exclude only temporary credential files that shouldn't sync
**/.env.tmp
**/.env.backup
**/secrets.tmp
**/config.tmp

# Still exclude some cloud provider session tokens (regenerated frequently)
**/.aws/cli/cache/
**/.gcloud/logs/
**/.azure/logs/

# === SYSTEM FILES ===
